      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "dc01fb14a3de4b72",
      "text": "Campbell, R. L., Brown, N. R., & DiBello, L. A., (1991).  The programmer's burden: Developing expertise in programming.  In R. R. Hoffman (Ed.), _The cognition of experts: Psychological research and emperical AI_ (pp. 269-294).  New Your: Springer-Verlag.\n\n"
